Package org.ietf.nea.pb.serialize.writer.bytebuffer

IETF TNCCS message byte buffer writers.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PbBatchHeaderWriter
    Writer to serialize a TNCCS batch header compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbMessageAccessRecommendationValueWriter
    Writer to serialize a TNCCS access recommendation message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbMessageAssessmentResultValueWriter
    Writer to serialize a TNCCS assessment result message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbMessageErrorParameterOffsetValueWriter
    Writer to serialize a TNCCS error parameter with an error offset compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbMessageErrorParameterVersionValueWriter
    Writer to serialize a TNCCS unsupported version error parameter compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbMessageErrorValueWriter
    Writer to serialize a TNCCS error message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbMessageExperimentalValueWriter
    Writer to serialize a TNCCS experimental message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbMessageHeaderWriter
    Writer to serialize a TNCCS message header compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbMessageImValueWriter
    Writer to serialize a TNCCS integrity measurement component message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbMessageLanguagePreferenceValueWriter
    Writer to serialize a TNCCS language preference message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbMessageReasonStringValueWriter
    Writer to serialize a TNCCS reason string message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbMessageRemediationParameterStringValueWriter
    Writer to serialize a TNCCS string remediation parameter compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbMessageRemediationParametersValueWriter
    Writer to serialize a TNCCS remediation parameters message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbMessageRemediationParameterUriValueWriter
    Writer to serialize a TNCCS URI remediation parameter compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbWriter
    Writer to serialize an entire TNCCS batch compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
    PbWriterFactory
    Factory utility to create a writer, that can serialize an entire TNCCS batch compliant to RFC 5793 from a Java object to a buffer of bytes.
